@startuml
[*] --> CreateAccount
CreateAccount --> Login
Login --> RegistrationSuccessful: #green
RegistrationSuccessful --> EndProcess
Login --> InvalidLocation: #red
InvalidLocation --> EndProcess
Login --> ValidLocation
ValidLocation --> ChooseWeatherInfo
ChooseWeatherInfo --> Temperature
Temperature --> ShowSelectedWeatherInfo
ShowSelectedWeatherInfo --> AdditionalDetails
AdditionalDetails --> Logout
Logout --> EndSession
EndSession --> [*]
@enduml
